4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for beginners to become cybersecurity specialists. This 16-week program includes three live online classes weekly, with a maximum class size of 16 participants. Students will gain foundational knowledge in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, along with expertise in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. The course covers risk management and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, participants receive an officially recognized 4Geeks Certificate. Classes are available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop